        <title>Hike Via Glaralpina, Etappe 07</title>
        <link>https://cssz.ch/events/hike-via-glaralpina-etappe-07/</link>
        <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 00:00:00 +0200</pubDate>
        
        <guid>https://cssz.ch/events/hike-via-glaralpina-etappe-07/</guid>
        <description>&lt;img src="https://cssz.ch/images/events/2024-09-01-hike-via-glaralpina-etappe-07/ricardo-gomez-angel-e2t8gAfW5rk-unsplash.jpg" alt="Featured image of post Hike Via Glaralpina, Etappe 07" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;A more chill hike this time, but still with a good amount of uphill.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;connection-there&#34;&gt;Connection there&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;06:43 &amp;ndash; 08:52 (&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://www.sbb.ch/en?date=%222024-09-01%22&amp;amp;moment=%22DEPARTURE%22&amp;amp;selected_trip=0&amp;amp;stops=%5B%7B%22value%22%3A%228503000%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22ID%22%2C%22label%22%3A%22Z%C3%BCrich%20HB%22%7D%2C%7B%22value%22%3A%228505776%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22ID%22%2C%22label%22%3A%22Urnerboden%2C%20Dorf%22%7D%5D&amp;amp;time=%2206%3A42%22&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Zürich HB → Urnerboden, Dorf&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;planned-route&#34;&gt;Planned route&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The route has a minimal variant which can optionally be extended by going closer to the Glattalpsee or even hiking/running around the lake.
Closer to the Glattalpsee, we can split into two groups: one going around the lake while the other one chills and waits for the first group.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Total distance:&lt;/strong&gt; 7.9 km, up to 13.2 km (with the lake loop)&lt;br&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Duration:&lt;/strong&gt; 5:30 h (minimal), up to 7:10 h (with the lake loop)&lt;br&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Uphill/downhill:&lt;/strong&gt; 980 m / 500 m&lt;br&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Difficulty:&lt;/strong&gt; Moderate&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;iframe style=&#34;border:none; width: 100%;&#34; src=&#34;https://en.frame.mapy.cz/s/hejetucuzu&#34; height=&#34;600&#34; frameborder=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;mb-4&#34;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;connection-back&#34;&gt;Connection back&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;depending on our hiking time, for example 17:02 &amp;ndash; 19:55 (&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://www.sbb.ch/en?date=%222024-09-01%22&amp;amp;moment=%22DEPARTURE%22&amp;amp;selected_trip=0&amp;amp;stops=%5B%7B%22value%22%3A%228530781%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22ID%22%2C%22label%22%3A%22Glattalp%22%7D%2C%7B%22value%22%3A%228503000%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22ID%22%2C%22label%22%3A%22Z%C3%BCrich%20HB%22%7D%5D&amp;amp;time=%2216%3A43%22&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Glattalp → Zürich HB&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The first leg is a cable car from Glattalp to Sahli, operated by &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://glattalp.ch/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Glattalp Luftseilbahn&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The ticket to the cable car (one-way descent) costs CHF 12 and must be bought on the spot (Twint or card)
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This means, when buying the SBB tickets, only get &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://www.sbb.ch/en?date=%222024-09-01%22&amp;amp;moment=%22DEPARTURE%22&amp;amp;selected_trip=0&amp;amp;stops=%5B%7B%22value%22%3A%228587691%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22ID%22%2C%22label%22%3A%22Bisisthal%2C%20Sahli%20Seilbahnstat.%22%7D%2C%7B%22value%22%3A%228503000%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22ID%22%2C%22label%22%3A%22Z%C3%BCrich%20HB%22%7D%5D&amp;amp;time=%2216%3A43%22&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Bisisthal, Sahli Seilbahnstat. → Zürich HB&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The latest available cable car listed by SBB is at 17:02, but the &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://glattalp.ch/fahrplan/&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Glattalp Fahrplan&lt;/a&gt; lists connections until 18:02&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description>
        </item>
